data.title: Program Highlights – Week 09/05/2016 to 15/05/2016

data.text:
All times are UTC/GMT

Monday 9

15:30

Live from Zakopane, Poland. Family of Radio Maryja Meeting and Holy Mass from the Shrine of Our Lady of Fatima in Krzeptówki.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV TRWAM

Tuesday 10

17:00

Live from Warsaw, Poland. Holy Mass for the victims of the Smolensk Air disaster of April 10, 2010, from St. John’s Archcathedral.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV TRWAM

Wednesday 11

08:00

Papal General Audience

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN, Telepace, TV2000, TRSP, K-TV Fernsehen, TV TRWAM, KTO

Streaming Online Live: Here via Vatican Player

Channels Broadcasting Delayed: EWTN (20:00), Canção Nova International (20:00), KTO (13:00, and again at 22:10)

11:30

Live from Wigratzbad, Bavaria, Germany. Holy Mass, Exposition of Blessed Sacrament and Blessing of the Sick, from the Gebetsstätte Wigratzbad.

Channels Broadcasting Live: K-TV Fernsehen

Streaming Online Live: Here via K-TV.org

Thursday 12

08:00

Live from Kevelaer, Germany. Holy Mass for Pilgrimage to Marienbasilika in Kevelaer, the Basilica of St. Mary, Comforter of the Sadnesses. Presided by Bishop Franz-Josef Overbeck, Bishop of Essen, Ordinary of the Military Ordinariate of Deutsches Militärordinariat.

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN Katholisches

Streaming Online Live: Here via EWTN.de

09:30

Live from Sala Stampa, Vatican City. Press Conference for the presentation of the Casa Italia Paralimpica a Rio 2016 (Italia Paralympic House in Rio 2016)

Streaming Online Live: Here via Vatican Player

15:30

Live form Ottawa, Canada. Complete Coverage of the Canadian National March for Life.

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN

Streaming Online Live: Here via EWTN.com

16:55

Live from Padua, Italy. Holy Mass for the 150th Anniversary of the Birth of St. Leopold Mandic, from the Shrine of St. Leopold Mandic.

Channels Broadcasting Live: Telepace

20:30

Live from Fatima, Portugal. Prayer Vigil, Procession, and Holy Mass for the May International Pilgrimage, on the Anniversary of the First Apparition of Our Lady. Blessing of the Candles and recitation of the Rosary in the Chapel of the Apparitions, followed by Candlelight Procession and finally celebration of Holy Mass. Presided by Manuel José Cardinal Macário do Nascimento Clemente, Patriarch of Lisbon.

Channels Broadcasting Live: Canção Nova Internacional, Telepace, K-TV Fernsehen, EWTN

Friday 13

08:30

Live from Fatima, Portugal. Recitation of the Rosary, Procession, Holy Mass and Blessing of the Sick for the May International Pilgrimage, on the Anniversary of the First Apparition of Our Lady. Presided by Manuel José Cardinal Macário do Nascimento Clemente, Patriarch of Lisbon.

Channels Broadcasting Live: Canção Nova Internacional, Telepace, K-TV Fernsehen, EWTN

11:00

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Coverage of the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

13:00

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Coverage of the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

14:30

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Holy Mass at the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

17:00

Live from Stötten am Auerberg, Germany. Holy Mass followed by May Devotions on the Feast of Our Lady of Fatima, from the Parish Church of Sts. Peter and Paul.

Channels Broadcasting Live: K-TV Fernsehen

19:00

Live from St. Paul, Minnesota, USA . Holy Mass for the Installation of Bernard Anthony Hebda, as Metropolitan Archbishop of Saint Paul and Minneapolis, from the Cathedral of St. Paul.

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN

Streaming Online Live: Here via EWTN.com

Saturday 14

08:00

Special Audience of Pope Francis with pilgrims in Rome for the Extraordinary Jubilee Holy Year of Mercy

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN, Telepace, TV2000, TRSP, K-TV Fernsehen, TV TRWAM, KTO

Streaming Online Live: Here via Vatican Player

09:30

Live from Studzieniczna, Poland. Holy Mass for the Children’s Rosary Group (Podwórkowych Kółek Różańcowych Dzieci), from the Shrine of Our Lady of Studzieniczna. Presided by Bishop Jerzy Mazur, S.V.D., Bishop of Ełk

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV TRWAM

11:30

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Coverage of the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

13:00

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Coverage of the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

14:00

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Holy Mass at the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

17:00

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Coverage of the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

19:00

Live from Paris, France. Holy Mass on the Vigil of the Solemnity of Pentecost, with Confirmation of Adults, from the Cathedral of Notre-Dame de Paris. Presided by André Cardinal Vingt-Trois, Archbishop of Paris.

Channels Broadcasting Live: KTO

Sunday 15

05:55

Live from Wigratzbad, Bavaria, Germany. Holy Mass in the Extraordinary Form of the Roman Rite, Solemn Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecosts, from the Sühnekirche, Gebetsstätte Wigratzbad

Channels Broadcasting Live: K-TV Fernsehen

06:30

Live from Jerusalem, Israel. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost at the 7th Catholic Charismatic Renewal Conference of Pentecost, from the Pontifical Institute Notre Dame of Jerusalem Centre.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com

07:00

Live from Bkerke, Lebanon. Divine Liturgy, in the Maronite Rite, on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Patriarchal Seat. Presided by Béchara Boutros Cardinal Raï, O.M.M., Patriarch of Antioch and the Whole Levant. (Maronite)

Channels Broadcasting Live: Noursat

Streaming Online Live: Here via Noursat.tv

08:00

Live from St. Peter’s Basilica, Vatican City. Papal Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost. Presided by Pope Francis.

Channels Broadcasting Live: Telepace, EWTN, TV2000, KTO, K-TV Fernsehen, TV TRWAM, TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via Vatican Player

09:00

Live from Cologne, Germany. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Kölner Dom, Cathedral of Sts. Peter and Paul. Presided by Rainer Maria Cardinal Woelki, Metropolitan Archbishop of Cologne

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN Katholisches

09:30

Live from San Giovanni Rotondo, Italy. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Pilgrimage Church of St. Pio of Pietrelcina.

Channels Broadcasting Live: Padre Pio TV

Streaming Online Live: Here via TeleRadioPadrePio.it

10:00

Papal Regina Caeli

Channels Broadcasting Live: Telepace, TV2000, K-TV Fernsehen, TV TRWAM, KTO, EWTN, Padre Pio TV, TRSP

Streaming Online Live: Here via Vatican Player

Channels Broadcasting Delayed: KTO (11:50), Canção Nova (14:30)

12:00

Live from Irondale, Alabama, USA. EWTN Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Chapel of Our Lady of the Angels.

Channels Broadcasting Live: EWTN

Streaming Online Live: Here via EWTN.com

16:30

Live from Paris, France. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Cathedral of Notre-Dame de Paris.

Channels Broadcasting Live: KTO

17:00

Live from Ziemetshausen, Germany. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost, from the Pilgrimage Church of Maria Vesperbild. Presided by Archbishop Thomas Edward Gullickson, Titular Archbishop of Polymartium, Apostolic Nuncio to Switzerland, Apostolic Nuncio to Liechtenstein

Channels Broadcasting Live: K-TV Fernsehen

18:00

Live from Cachoeira Paulista, São Paulo, Brazil. Holy Mass on the Solemnity of Pentecost from the Accampamento de Pentecostes.

Channels Broadcasting Live: TV Canção Nova

Streaming Online Live: Here via TV.CançãoNova.com
